 />\n祈求 民主 與自由 萬世都 不朽<br />\n我願 榮光 歸香港<br />\n<br />\nYoutube MV<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=9e25f2e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y</a><br />\n<br />\n純音樂<br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/dgx-dgx/anthem-ver31\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fdgx-dgx%2Fanthem-ver31&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=09524d92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/dgx-dgx/anthem-ver31</a><br />\n<br />\n通場加映<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Organ 管風琴版 </span></span><br />\nBy 高學歷廢青巴打<br />\n（好神聖高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽完再喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/dr-rubbish-teen/hong-kong-anthem-organ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fdr-rubbish-teen%2Fhong-kong-anthem-organ&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=b146efce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/dr-rubbish-teen/hong-kong-anthem-organ</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>想幫手手足，記得去機場集合啦！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n如果想幫更多既手足，可以入Google留TG ID！<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/XLCnYwWNq2B7Jkqw8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FXLCnYwWNq2B7Jkqw8&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=e735a805\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/XLCnYwWNq2B7Jkqw8</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">之後會有新音樂，<br />\n請mon post/ subscribe/<br />\n支持Dgx巴打</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/